      "span_text": "HCMV mutant virus AD169US2-US11 (deletion of US2 to US11) and RV670 (deletion of IRS to US11, but contains only US10) were provided by A.E. Campbell (Eastern Virginia Medical School, Norfolk, Virginia; [CITATION_1] .",
